{"tid":1742633,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實好鐘意返工 一啲問題都無。","createTime":"2019-11-21T01:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T04:45:40.000Z","uid":216800,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8477b254c0705d71ddf5fadfb0db2b9fecc4c6ff","tid":1742633,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:03:43.000Z","msg":"小弟我休息咗幾日，今日好返就返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到地黨鐵，嘩屌 好撚多人<br />\n個個都塞喺門口度<br />\n入唔到去果啲個個都屌晒鬼：<br />\n入邊有無位呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行入啲啦屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲到啦屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英明神武嘅我，眼睛向左一望過去 <br />\n屌嗰邊咪有位囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我滋悠悠行過去嗰對關左好多次都未生到嘅門<br />\n慣性動作一轉身 <br />\n嘩屌，一堆人衝晒過黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住係咁推鳩我入去<br />\n行入啲啦屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲到啦屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入邊有無位呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地有無第二句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩左成十零分鐘 終於上晒車<br />\n心思細膩嘅我留意到啲人想屌又無位入<br />\n谷住谷住個樣 好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終於開到車嘅時候 心諗應該唔會遲到啦呱<br />\n仆街，班人搭一個站就落晒車 衝晒去對面線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住對面又有班人落車衝晒過黎又推過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我車啲人呆撚晒<br />\n又是者又玩左十零分鐘先開到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻，<br />\n睿智嘅我心諗聽日要早啲出門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔係一定遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家返工記得提早啲出門呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc77ee10dc787c05f6e9249e325258b392ccc3b","tid":1742633,"uid":306826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:04:39.000Z","msg":"阻你地少少時間 有關選舉問題可以睇以下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n0成本截斷建制藍絲收入 (下)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"49c6a9fa670d78dd031a6f13bb6d13d58b5449fe","tid":1742633,"uid":65629,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:05:48.000Z","msg":"仲有Raymond 哥撞你落車添<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jAHRmdV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjAHRmdV.jpg&h=cb2da986&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c28b7c4e2d573efb7a327f51c74fd5e3753a3d1","tid":1742633,"uid":321684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:18:08.000Z","msg":"手足你冇事太好了"},{"pid":"24d6f37044dd91296ac2bbdaa9fb9c652bf645c7","tid":1742633,"uid":216800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:19:53.000Z","msg":"呀係<br />\n原本喺我隔離撩鼻屎撩得好開心嘅阿姐<br />\n比班人一推 成隻手指插咗入去<br />\n望住都覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個表情好似中咗輻射咁👉🏻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a7c3eeeaa82873894a2556bc86ca6d2954dea1","tid":1742633,"uid":216800,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6c28b7c4e2d573efb7a327f51c74fd5e3753a3d1","tid":1742633,"uid":321684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:18:08.000Z","msg":"手足你冇事太好了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:22:44.000Z","msg":"多謝你地，我地小隊全部生還<br />\n我會將啲經驗全部講晒比你地知"},{"pid":"fe7ada780f794e469b9706a432f269c4ce231a05","tid":1742633,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:24:05.000Z","msg":"唔明你講咩"},{"pid":"0c26519901490a1f7a65cee869ad294fae994f87","tid":1742633,"uid":321684,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"82a7c3eeeaa82873